e-developed-world-new-report-shows/0000018c-b055-d45c-a98e-bb5d02af0000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫高中校长因同情加沙人的苦难而面临停职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-high-school-principal-faces-suspension-for-sympathizing-with-suffering-of-gazans/0000018c-b09c-db94-afbd-b0fd76a80000</link><description>校长因在 Facebook 页面上发表《国土报》的文章而被传唤参加听证会，该文章批评以色列媒体对加沙人道主义危机缺乏报道</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 15:20:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-high-school-principal-faces-suspension-for-sympathizing-with-suffering-of-gazans/0000018c-b09c-db94-afbd-b0fd76a80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院规定，国家不能歧视想要收养的同性伴侣</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-cant-discriminate-against-same-sex-couples-looking-to-adopt-top-court-rules/0000018c-b0d2-d014-a3cd-bade63a80000</link><description>高等法院裁定，在收养孩子的过程中，异性恋不应优先于同性伴侣</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 14:57:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-cant-discriminate-against-same-sex-couples-looking-to-adopt-top-court-rules/0000018c-b0d2-d014-a3cd-bade63a80000</guid></item><item><title>纳粹掠夺了她的艺术品。 10月7日，哈马斯又偷走了另一件雕塑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/museums-exhibits/2023-12-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-nazis-looted-her-sculpture-on-october-7-hamas-stole-another-piece/0000018c-afbb-d45c-a98e-afffd7710000</link><description>80 年前被纳粹掠夺的一位法国犹太先驱艺术家的作品究竟属于一位来自伦敦的犹太妇女还是该艺术家的孙女？这件事和10月7日的事件有什么关系呢？</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 14:56:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/museums-exhibits/2023-12-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-nazis-looted-her-sculpture-on-october-7-hamas-stole-another-piece/0000018c-afbb-d45c-a98e-afffd7710000</guid></item><item><title>联合国报告对西岸权利“迅速恶化”表示遗憾</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/un-report-deplores-rapid-deterioration-of-rights-in-west-bank/0000018c-b07c-db94-afbd-b07d3aa50000</link><description>报道称，自10月7日哈马斯袭击以来，约300名巴勒斯坦人在与以色列军队或极端主义定居者的冲突中丧生。联合国专员呼吁以色列确保“有效保护巴勒斯坦社区”</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 13:30:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/un-report-deplores-rapid-deterioration-of-rights-in-west-bank/0000018c-b07c-db94-afbd-b07d3aa50000</guid></item><item><title>尼尔奥兹幸存者离开埃拉特酒店，可能不会再回家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/nir-oz-survivors-leave-eilat-hotel-face-likelihood-they-wont-be-going-home-again/0000018c-af93-d45c-a98e-afdfcd590000</link><description>“当我们的生活被打破的那一天”和“国家抛弃了我们，好人就在它的位置上” ■ 在酒店找到避难所后，幸存者形成了一种奇怪的新常态，日子过得没有时间表或例行公事—— “长湿婆”为他们失去的一切</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 12:53:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/nir-oz-survivors-leave-eilat-hotel-face-likelihood-they-wont-be-going-home-again/0000018c-af93-d45c-a98e-afdfcd590000</guid></item><item><title>Nova狂欢受害者的家属拒绝再保持沉默</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-families-of-the-victims-at-the-reim-party-refuse-to-keep-silent-any-longed/0000018c-acff-d22c-a98c-fcff58b50000</link><description>大屠杀发生后的几个星期里，被害者的父母保持沉默，因悲痛而瘫痪。现在，140 个家庭聚集在一起，要求以色列领导人给出答案。 “没有人有精力去战斗，但我们别无选择。我们被遗弃了，”一位家长说</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 12:52:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-families-of-the-victims-at-the-reim-party-refuse-to-keep-silent-any-longed/0000018c-acff-d22c-a98c-fcff58b50000</guid></item><item><title>泄露的法院判决：内塔尼亚胡的司法政变卷土重来，他的攻击再次爆发</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/leaked-court-decision-netanyahus-judicial-coup-is-back-and-his-attacks-are-unleashed/0000018c-b00a-d45c-a98e-bb4e27290000</link><description>就像美国最高法院关于堕胎裁决的泄密一样，以色列法官对内塔尼亚胡关键司法政变法案的泄密立场值得调查</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 12:20:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/leaked-court-decision-netanyahus-judicial-coup-is-back-and-his-attacks-are-unleashed/0000018c-b00a-d45c-a98e-bb4e27290000</guid></item><item><title>星巴克如何卷入以色列-哈马斯战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/how-starbucks-got-embroiled-in-the-israel-hamas-war/0000018c-b043-db94-afbd-b07b8ef20000</link><description>欢迎来到 BDS 2.0：如果你不能抵制一家以色列公司，那就以最站不住脚的理由寻找其他东西来抵制</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 12:04:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/how-starbucks-got-embroiled-in-the-israel-hamas-war/0000018c-b043-db94-afbd-b07b8ef20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列宣布约旦河西岸货币兑换恐怖组织扣押哈马斯数百万资金</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-declares-west-bank-money-exchange-terror-org-seizes-millions-of-hamas-funds/0000018c-aff3-db94-afbd-affb65040000</link><description>以色列军队突袭了约旦河西岸的 9 个货币兑换分行，逮捕了 21 名涉嫌向哈马斯和伊斯兰圣战组织转移资金的巴勒斯坦人。巴勒斯坦人报告说，袭击期间发生冲突，造成一人死亡、多人受伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 11:33:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-declares-west-bank-money-exchange-terror-org-seizes-millions-of-hamas-funds/0000018c-aff3-db94-afbd-affb65040000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗革命卫队主席誓言在以色列杀害高级顾问后“铲除犹太复国主义政权”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/irgc-chief-vows-to-eradicate-zionist-regime-after-alleged-israeli-killing-of-top-adviser/0000018c-afe2-d45c-a98e-afeee70e0000</link><description>伊朗最高领袖哈梅内伊在叙利亚空袭中丧生的赛义德·拉齐·穆萨维的葬礼上主持祈祷。以色列军队拒绝就穆萨维之死发表评论，但表示已采取一切必要行动来保卫国家</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 11:09:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/irgc-chief-vows-to-eradicate-zionist-regime-after-alleged-israeli-killing-of-top-adviser/0000018c-afe2-d45c-a98e-afeee70e0000</guid></item><item><title>当 DNA 失败时，这些以色列人类学家正在帮助识别 10 月 7 日死者的身份</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/when-dna-fails-these-israeli-anthropologists-are-helping-identify-the-october-7-dead/0000018c-afe7-d45c-a98e-afef12ea0000</link><description>Israel Hershkovitz 教授、Hila May 博士和特拉维夫大学的体质人类学专家正在与法医病理学家合作，帮助识别 10 月 7 日的受害者并确定他们的死因，并为未来针对哈马斯恐怖分子建立案件</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 10:55:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/when-dna-fails-these-israeli-anthropologists-are-helping-identify-the-october-7-dead/0000018c-afe7-d45c-a98e-afef12ea0000</guid></item><item><title>这位犹太学者认为散居海外的犹太人必须接受流亡才能拯救犹太教</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-12-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-jewish-scholar-believes-diaspora-jews-must-embrace-exile-to-save-judaism/0000018c-af75-d45c-a98e-af7d47ac0000</link><description>绍尔·马吉德曾经倾向于犹太人定居点，但如今他是一位受人尊敬的犹太研究教授，他将自己的世界观定义为“反犹太复国主义”。他的立场设想以色列尊重所有人民的历史并放弃犹太复国主义作为“仅限犹太人”的意识形态</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 10:48:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-12-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-jewish-scholar-believes-diaspora-jews-must-embrace-exile-to-save-judaism/0000018c-af75-d45c-a98e-af7d47ac0000</guid></item><item><title>决定泄露后以色列最高法院将加快对司法政变法的裁决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-top-court-justices-set-to-expedite-ruling-on-judicial-coup-law-after-decision-leak/0000018c-af76-db94-afbd-af7f3c1b0000</link><description>报告称，八名法官中的大多数支持废除该法律，七名法官反对。司法部长亚里夫·莱文回应称，高等法院不应“在战争期间发布有争议的裁决，即使是在其法官之间”</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 09:55:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-top-court-justices-set-to-expedite-ruling-on-judicial-coup-law-after-decision-leak/0000018c-af76-db94-afbd-af7f3c1b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵惊醒后开枪，轻伤战友</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-opens-fire-after-waking-up-with-a-start-lightly-wounds-fellow-troops/0000018c-ac24-d22d-a3dd-bd7d13250000</link><description>由于这名士兵的健康状况，尚未就该事件接受军队询问。每天都有数十名士兵被带出加沙接受心理健康官员和精神病医生的检查和治疗</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 08:04:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-opens-fire-after-waking-up-with-a-start-lightly-wounds-fellow-troops/0000018c-ac24-d22d-a3dd-bd7d13250000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了周三在加沙战斗中丧生的三名以色列士兵的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/idf-names-three-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-fighting-on-wednesday/0000018c-af30-db94-afbd-af79141f0000</link><description>以色列军方还表示，加沙地带南部和中部还有其他士兵受重伤。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 07:38:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/idf-names-three-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-fighting-on-wednesday/0000018c-af30-db94-afbd-af79141f0000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗“独立”代理人的袭击增加了与以色列和美国发生直接冲突的可能性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/attacks-by-irans-independent-proxies-increase-odds-of-direct-clash-with-israel-and-u-s/0000018c-ad16-d22d-a3dd-bd7f52010000</link><description>自以色列与哈马斯战争爆发以来，德黑兰一直避免与以色列和美国直接对抗。但“抵抗轴心”成员所表现出的独立性使得伊斯兰共和国更难维持合理的推诿，并有可能将其拖入冲突</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 04:00:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/attacks-by-irans-independent-proxies-increase-odds-of-direct-clash-with-israel-and-u-s/0000018c-ad16-d22d-a3dd-bd7f52010000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯大屠杀后，以色列极端正统派部长花了一天时间为地方选举进行政治活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/haredi-israeli-minister-spent-day-after-hamas-massacre-politicking-for-local-election/0000018c-ace9-d22c-a98c-fced9a040000</link><description>当以色列陷入混乱时，梅厄·波鲁什正忙着做交易，以确保他的联合托拉犹太教党和他的儿子埃拉德市长以色列·波鲁什在即将到来的选举中的利益</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 04:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/haredi-israeli-minister-spent-day-after-hamas-massacre-politicking-for-local-election/0000018c-ace9-d22c-a98c-fced9a040000</guid></item></channel></rss>